PROBLEM 29: Maximum Depth of Binary Tree (LeetCode 104) - FREQUENCY: 10/10
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Given root of binary tree, return its maximum depth (number of nodes along 
longest path from root down to farthest leaf).

Example: [3,9,20,null,null,15,7] -> 3
"""
def max_depth(root):
